DE_PORTUCAL
 THE REMAKE! Well, the original version of this map was made by Pingo. I loved the map, and I thoungh it had A Lot of potencial. So I decided to come with this version. This was my biggest project to this date DIFERENCES: - Re_Textured; - Players can go on the roofs; - Added 3D_Sky Box; - Coveres all the map and blocking brushes with PlayerClip tool; - Little diference in the layout; - Added Props; - More detailed; - Tryed to optimize the map so much has I could to get higher FPS; - Realistic effects; I Hope you like this version, credits to Pingo_Tinto for letting me remake his map. NOTE: The rar. file is now on! (Credits to ma bro Chizbone.)
